	(203,'AirHelp','When Airlines Screw Up Your Flight, AirHelp (YC W14) Gets You Paid',158,'My wife and I had our flight from Europe to Japan cancelled a few summers ago. The put us another flight via Bangkok. Added 8 hours to our journey. That became a really long trip.Eventually we got the EU paperwork and filled it in meticulously. And to our surprise ?600 each arrived within a few weeks.As soon as the use of these type of apps become the norm the flight prices will probably go up a bit to compensate. Or maybe the airlines will be less cavalier about cancelling flights.',-1.00,17,'Operating','Get money when the airlines screw up your flight','2014','Winter',17000.00,'San Francisco','http://a2.images.crunchbase.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_98,w_98/v1397186604/d69b8c839351dff7843c444f0ed5b827.png','http://www.seed-db.com/companies/view?companyid=5697940240728064','http://www.crunchbase.com/organization/airhelp','http://www.getairhelp.com','Not Operating',0.800,'Y Combinator','','Transportation, Legal','https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=7349175'),
