	(214,'Bannerman','Bannerman (YC S14) Delivers Bouncers On Demand',87,'We hired a bannerman guard for a party in downtown San Francisco on the weekend. The guy arrived half an hour early and was courteous and effective. Highlights included him preventing people standing outside our place on the streets with open drinks (which the police had previously warned us for) and him keeping someone we had to eject from the party out. We used to DIY security which was unreliable and risky as hosts became more drunk.',-0.20,13,'Operating','On Demand Private Security','2014','Summer',120000.00,'San Francisco','http://a3.images.crunchbase.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_98,w_98/v1397184037/172e39ce4628ce0f77a91906fadf2e41.jpg','http://www.seed-db.com/companies/view?companyid=5766504226226176','http://www.crunchbase.com/organization/bannerman','http://getbannerman.com','Not Operating',0.533,'Y Combinator','','Curated Web','https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=7901733'),
