	(289,'HauteDay','HauteDay (YC S14), A Gamified Shopping Site',14,'I skimmed the article, clicked through to http://hauteday.com, and shrugged. It wasn\'t until I read the About Us page that I got why this is actually interesting. Seriously guys, if you\'re reading this, your current tag line doesn\'t work. Right now it says:    Each day our community votes on the hautest\\n    new finds in fashion.\\n\\nAnd instead it should say:    Find the hautest new clothes, and we\'ll buy them for you.\\n\\nI\'m really, really confused about why you\'re burying the lede. I\'m also grimacing at the use of the non-word \"hautest\".Rule 1 of any website: your greatest competitor is the back button. If you can\'t sell a visitor on what you\'re offering almost immediately, you\'re going to lose them.Rule 2: It\'s not about you, it\'s about me. No one cares about your community. People care about getting free shit (and winning), especially if that free shit is a free pair of Adriano Goldschmied skinny jeans.I\'d love a free pair of AG jeans. So let me know when you launch this for men ;)',0.38,3,'Operating','Haute Day was created to make shopping a lot more fun!','2014','Summer',120000.00,'','http://a2.images.crunchbase.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_98,w_98/v1408517870/zvyaemisqvg6db81c4q9.png','http://www.seed-db.com/companies/view?companyid=5674999679549440','http://www.crunchbase.com/organization/hauteday','http://hauteday.com/','Operating',0.525,'Y Combinator','','Shopping','https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=8195344'),
